    <description>Twigs densely short-hairy and with longer, white hairs. Leaf blade surfaces densely
        short-hairy abaxially (and sometimes adaxially). Immature inflorescence axes glabrous or
        hairy, sometimes glandular (not densely glandular-hairy). Ovaries densely
        hairy.</description>
    <phenology>Flowering winter–early spring</phenology>
